{"title":"Feedback Sports Velo Hinge 2.0 Updates Classic Home Wall Storage For Modern Bikes","link":"https://bikerumor.com/feedback-sports-velo-hinge-2-0-updates-classic-home-wall-storage-for-modern-bikes/","date":1701729141000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_at-home-on-the-wall.jpg\" alt=\"Feedback Sports Velo Hinge 2 adjustable home wall bike storage hook, at home bicycle on the wall\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_at-home-on-the-wall.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_at-home-on-the-wall-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_at-home-on-the-wall-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_at-home-on-the-wall-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_at-home-on-the-wall-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_at-home-on-the-wall-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_at-home-on-the-wall-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Ten years on, a new Feedback Sports Velo Hinge 2.0 overhauls their simple but popular bike wall hook with an upgraded version that works with all of your latest bikes. Stronger construction to hang heavier bikes: ✓. Longer hook for deeper aero rims: ✓. Wider hinge &amp; wider rear wheel bumper for even plus-sized mountain bikes: ✓. What more do you need?</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Feedback Sports Velo Hinge 2.0 home wall bike storage hook</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook.jpg\" alt=\"Feedback Sports Velo Hinge 2 adjustable home wall bike storage hook, detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos/Feedback)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Feedback Velo Hinge is incredibly simple in pairing a classic hook to hang your bike from its front wheel AND putting that hook on a hinge so you can angle the bike towards the wall to take up less space. Line a few up next to each other and you can flip through your bikes like they’re on a rolodex, without them always sticking 3 feet (a meter) out into the room.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_hand-and-fold.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_hand-and-fold.jpg\" alt=\"Feedback Sports Velo Hinge 2 adjustable home wall bike storage hook, hand and swing\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_hand-and-fold.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_hand-and-fold-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_hand-and-fold-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_hand-and-fold-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_hand-and-fold-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_hand-and-fold-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Since we first spotted it at Interbike just over a decade ago, the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/ib13-feedback-sports-sweet-truing-stand-w-disc-brake-rotor-guide-fat-bike-stands-more/\" target=\"_blank\">original Velo Hinge</a> has been a Feedback favorite for simple, efficient at-home bike storage. I mean who doesn’t want to show off their bike at home? Yet still easily hang it up and pull it off the wall to ride. Then, push it back against the wall to minimize lost space.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And now, Feedback gives the Velo Hinge 2.0 a few simple upgrades making it better than ever.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>What’s new in version 2.0? </h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_in-detail.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_in-detail.jpg\" alt=\"Feedback Sports Velo Hinge 2 adjustable home wall bike storage hook, new size\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_in-detail.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_in-detail-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_in-detail-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_in-detail-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_in-detail-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_in-detail-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new coated steel Feedback Velo Hinge 2.0 features a stiffer, stronger hinge body and a longer wheel hook. The new design uses a burlier full-length weld-reinforced hinge for “flex-free bike mounting” and smoother pivoting movement. It now boasts a “secure load capacity” of 50lb/22.7kg when you properly mount it into a stud or other secure wall fixture. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_up-close.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1700\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_up-close.jpg\" alt=\"Feedback Sports Velo Hinge 2 adjustable home wall bike storage hook, deep carbon rims\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_up-close.jpg 1700w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_up-close-297x262.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_up-close-800x706.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_up-close-120x106.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_up-close-768x678.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_up-close-1536x1355.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Then, the wider hook means you can now hook a 29″ Plus mountain bike tire up to 3″ wide. Or you can now fit deep section aero road wheels, up to 99mm deep when combining rim and tire overall depth. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_Tire-Rim-Compatibility.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_Tire-Rim-Compatibility.jpg\" alt=\"Feedback Sports Velo Hinge 2 adjustable home wall bike storage hook, tire &amp; rim compatability\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_Tire-Rim-Compatibility.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_Tire-Rim-Compatibility-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_Tire-Rim-Compatibility-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_Tire-Rim-Compatibility-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_Tire-Rim-Compatibility-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_Tire-Rim-Compatibility-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em>For reference</em>, the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/new-zipp-303-s-wheels-get-complete-redesign-wider-hookless-more-aero-less-expensive/\" target=\"_blank\">Zipp 303s</a> with 2.25″ MTB tires on my <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/3t-extrema-italia-carbon-29er-adventure-gravel-bike/\" target=\"_blank\">3T Extrema test bike</a> are 99mm. 40mm tires on the same wheels are just 76mm. And 30mm road tires on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/first-impressions-up-close-in-the-wind-tunnel-w-dt-swiss-arc-aero-wheel-redesign/\" target=\"_blank\">DT ARC 50</a> wheels measure just 78mm deep overall.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The updated Velo Hinge 2.0 also adds grip tape to that top plate where your tire sits against the hinge for extra stability. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_lower-wheel-support.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_lower-wheel-support.jpg\" alt=\"Feedback Sports Velo Hinge 2 adjustable home wall bike storage hook, lower support\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_lower-wheel-support.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_lower-wheel-support-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_lower-wheel-support-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_lower-wheel-support-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_lower-wheel-support-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_lower-wheel-support-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And there’s still the simple rear wheel bumper. But, now a bit larger to stabilize the bike against the way as you pivot, without skipping along the wall.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mount the hinge in either direction to pivot your bike left or right, out of the way. And fold the hook flat when not in use storing a bike for a clean, uncluttered look.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Upgraded Feedback Velo Hinge 2.0 – Pricing &amp; availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_studio-folded.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_studio-folded.jpg\" alt=\"Feedback Sports Velo Hinge 2 adjustable home wall bike storage hook, studio\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_studio-folded.jpg 1500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_studio-folded-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_studio-folded-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_studio-folded-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_studio-folded-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_studio-folded-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The completely upgraded Feedback Sports Velo Hinge 2.0 bicycle wall storage hook is available now in the US for $40. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_relax-at-home-with-your-bicycle.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_relax-at-home-with-your-bicycle.jpg\" alt=\"Feedback Sports Velo Hinge 2 adjustable home wall bike storage hook, relax at hoem with your bicycle\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_relax-at-home-with-your-bicycle.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_relax-at-home-with-your-bicycle-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_relax-at-home-with-your-bicycle-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_relax-at-home-with-your-bicycle-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_relax-at-home-with-your-bicycle-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Feedback-Sports-Velo-Hinge-2-adjustable-home-wall-bike-storage-hook_relax-at-home-with-your-bicycle-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Worldwide availability is expected by the middle of this month with EU pricing of 45€.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://feedbacksports.com/\" target=\"_blank\">FeedbackSports.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/feedback-sports-velo-hinge-2-0-updates-classic-home-wall-storage-for-modern-bikes/\">Feedback Sports Velo Hinge 2.0 Updates Classic Home Wall Storage For Modern Bikes</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"5b01a74d7921b81713525720ae7cf0ae84419024175d156a0e612daf1fbaf0d1","category":"Cycling"}